messages.messageBody:
*********
I forgot I wanted to tell you guys that my friend did decide make the big
splurge and take her son to London for the Led Zeppelin concert. Isn't that
cool?!

********

YEA!!!!!

********
So, just so we don't miss out on another valuable connection by not asking
-- anybody happen to have any ideas of other fun things to do in London with a
15-year old weapon-collecting Led Zeppelin fan?

Patty

********

The Tower of London houses an armory which is awesome. It also houses the Crown Jewels, and not too mention the gory history of the place. Well worth a visit.




Meghan

messages.messageBody:
I forgot I wanted to tell you guys that my friend did decide make the big
splurge and take her son to London for the Led Zeppelin concert. Isn't that
cool?!

Funny other thing though, when she read the advice I sent her she also saw
the posts about the gun, and instantly messaged me asking if Sam still needed
one. Turns out that same son has a big collection of them. So, the
connection was there but I just didn't think to make it.

So, just so we don't miss out on another valuable connection by not asking
-- anybody happen to have any ideas of other fun things to do in London with a
15-year old weapon-collecting Led Zeppelin fan?

Patty
